{"id": 1704, "genre": 1000, "title": "消费过后，你通常是一个什么样的评论选手？", "description": "“老好人型”，还是“路见不平一声吼”型？（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 11585, "comment_count": 32, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170525145327EsUBRIoNLrptKqb2.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-05-26T17:00:09Z", "questions": [{"id": 2352, "title": "消费过后，你通常是一个什么样的评论选手？", "content": "消费过后，你通常是一个什么样的评论选手？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 207446, "content": "只有被店家气得不行的时候才会出手给差评", "image": "img/option/option/20170526102043ZkC0y6UiawIPF9Ag.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 207447, "content": "体验好到超乎预期的时候也会评论一下", "image": "img/option/option/20170526102506i51EZgrIdUHsV0Bt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 207449, "content": "图文并茂，非常详细，主要为了记录给自己看", "image": "img/option/option/20170526103224xy6QIAHC5keRh0Mn.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 207452, "content": "热情，评论区聊天爱好者，热衷于咨询他人或者回答咨询", "image": "img/option/option/201705261443249uXEJOqQSbiczsCU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 207453, "content": "习惯性好评，想都不想就直接五星", "image": "img/option/option/20170526143322x4dsTQ8Sfqy9Nmn6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 207455, "content": "需要借助外力才愿意动手，比如有积分赠品或者店家苦苦央求", "image": "img/option/option/20170526132320M5kFJW8XdTKjpvGz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 207456, "content": "冷漠，基本没评论过", "image": "img/option/option/20170526142900fc1TYRCOo2y8k0dm.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 207457, "content": "有心无力，觉得应该评论一下但经常忘记或者注意不到", "image": "img/option/option/20170526132547n2kxH3iBDwfzhY6P.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}